{"id":143,"ayahs":[{"number":119,"arabic":"وَمَا لَكُمْ أَلَّا تَأْكُلُوا۟ مِمَّا ذُكِرَ ٱسْمُ ٱللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ وَقَدْ فَصَّلَ لَكُم مَّا حَرَّمَ عَلَيْكُمْ إِلَّا مَا ٱضْطُرِرْتُمْ إِلَيْهِ ۗ وَإِنَّ كَثِيرًۭا لَّيُضِلُّونَ بِأَهْوَآئِهِم بِغَيْرِ عِلْمٍ ۗ إِنَّ رَبَّكَ هُوَ أَعْلَمُ بِٱلْمُعْتَدِينَ","translation":"And why should you not eat of that over which God's name has been pronounced, seeing that He has so clearly spelled out to you what He has forbidden you [to eat] unless you are compelled [to do so]? But, behold, [it is precisely in such matters that] many people lead others astray by their own errant views, without [having any real] knowledge. Verily, thy Sustainer is fully aware of those who transgress the bounds of what is right.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/908.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":76147,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং কি হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76148,"position":2,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76149,"position":3,"arabic":"أَلَّا","translation":"যে না","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76150,"position":4,"arabic":"تَأْكُلُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা খাও","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76151,"position":5,"arabic":"مِمَّا","translation":"তা হতে (যার উপর)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76152,"position":6,"arabic":"ذُكِرَ","translation":"হয়েছে নেয়া","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76153,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱسْمُ","translation":"নাম","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76154,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌র","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76155,"position":9,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","translation":"উপর তার","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76156,"position":10,"arabic":"وَقَدْ","translation":"অথচ নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76157,"position":11,"arabic":"فَصَّلَ","translation":"তিনি বিস্তারিত বিবৃত করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76158,"position":12,"arabic":"لَكُم","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76159,"position":13,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76160,"position":14,"arabic":"حَرَّمَ","translation":"নিষিদ্ধ করেছেন (আল্লাহ্‌)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76161,"position":15,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ","translation":"উপর তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76162,"position":16,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"তবে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76163,"position":17,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76164,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱضْطُرِرْتُمْ","translation":"নিরুপায় হয়ে যাও তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76165,"position":19,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِ ۗ","translation":"দিকে তার (সেটা ভিন্ন কথা)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76167,"position":20,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76168,"position":21,"arabic":"كَثِيرًۭا","translation":"অনেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76169,"position":22,"arabic":"لَّيُضِلُّونَ","translation":"অবশ্যই পথভ্রষ্ট করে(অন্যকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76170,"position":23,"arabic":"بِأَهْوَآئِهِم","translation":"তাদের খেয়াল খুশী দ্বারা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76171,"position":24,"arabic":"بِغَيْرِ","translation":"ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76172,"position":25,"arabic":"عِلْمٍ ۗ","translation":"কোনো জ্ঞান (অর্থাৎ অজ্ঞতাবশত)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76174,"position":26,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76175,"position":27,"arabic":"رَبَّكَ","translation":"তোমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76176,"position":28,"arabic":"هُوَ","translation":"তিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76177,"position":29,"arabic":"أَعْلَمُ","translation":"খুব জানেন","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76178,"position":30,"arabic":"بِٱلْمُعْتَدِينَ","translation":"সম্পর্কে সীমালঙ্ঘনকারীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_119_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76179,"position":31,"arabic":"١١٩","translation":"(১১৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":120,"arabic":"وَذَرُوا۟ ظَٰهِرَ ٱلْإِثْمِ وَبَاطِنَهُۥٓ ۚ إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ يَكْسِبُونَ ٱلْإِثْمَ سَيُجْزَوْنَ بِمَا كَانُوا۟ يَقْتَرِفُونَ","translation":"But abstain from sinning, be it open or secret-for, behold, those who commit sins shall be requited for all that they have earned.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/909.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":76404,"position":1,"arabic":"وَذَرُوا۟","translation":"এবং তোমরা বর্জন করো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_120_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76405,"position":2,"arabic":"ظَـٰهِرَ","translation":"প্রকাশ্য","audioUrl":"wbw/006_120_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76406,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْإِثْمِ","translation":"পাপের কাজ","audioUrl":"wbw/006_120_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76407,"position":4,"arabic":"وَبَاطِنَهُۥٓ ۚ","translation":"এবং গোপন তার(কাজও)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_120_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76409,"position":5,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/006_120_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76410,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_120_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76411,"position":7,"arabic":"يَكْسِبُونَ","translation":"উপার্জন করে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_120_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76412,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْإِثْمَ","translation":"পাপ","audioUrl":"wbw/006_120_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76413,"position":9,"arabic":"سَيُجْزَوْنَ","translation":"অচিরেই তাদের প্রতিদান দেয়া হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_120_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76414,"position":10,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"বিনিময়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_120_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76415,"position":11,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","translation":"তারা ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_120_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76416,"position":12,"arabic":"يَقْتَرِفُونَ","translation":"তারা কুকর্ম করতে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_120_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76417,"position":13,"arabic":"١٢٠","translation":"(১২০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":121,"arabic":"وَلَا تَأْكُلُوا۟ مِمَّا لَمْ يُذْكَرِ ٱسْمُ ٱللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ وَإِنَّهُۥ لَفِسْقٌۭ ۗ وَإِنَّ ٱلشَّيَٰطِينَ لَيُوحُونَ إِلَىٰٓ أَوْلِيَآئِهِمْ لِيُجَٰدِلُوكُمْ ۖ وَإِنْ أَطَعْتُمُوهُمْ إِنَّكُمْ لَمُشْرِكُونَ","translation":"Hence, eat not of that over which God's name has not been pronounced: for this would be sinful conduct indeed. And, verily, the evil impulses [within men's hearts] whisper unto those who have made them their own that they should involve you in argument [as to what is and what is not a sin]; and if you pay heed unto them, lo! you will become [like] those who ascribe divinity to other beings or forces beside God.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/910.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":76513,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76514,"position":2,"arabic":"تَأْكُلُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা খেয়ো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76515,"position":3,"arabic":"مِمَّا","translation":"তা হতে (যার উপর)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76516,"position":4,"arabic":"لَمْ","translation":"নি","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76517,"position":5,"arabic":"يُذْكَرِ","translation":"নেয়া হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76518,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱسْمُ","translation":"নাম","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76519,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌র","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76520,"position":8,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","translation":"উপর তার","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76521,"position":9,"arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই তা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76522,"position":10,"arabic":"لَفِسْقٌۭ ۗ","translation":"অবশ্যই পাপ","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76524,"position":11,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76525,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلشَّيَـٰطِينَ","translation":"শয়তানরা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76526,"position":13,"arabic":"لَيُوحُونَ","translation":"অবশ্যই উস্কানি দেয়","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76527,"position":14,"arabic":"إِلَىٰٓ","translation":"প্রতি","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76528,"position":15,"arabic":"أَوْلِيَآئِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের বন্ধুদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76529,"position":16,"arabic":"لِيُجَـٰدِلُوكُمْ ۖ","translation":"যেন তারা ঝগড়া করে তোমাদের (সাথে)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76531,"position":17,"arabic":"وَإِنْ","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76532,"position":18,"arabic":"أَطَعْتُمُوهُمْ","translation":"তোমরা আনুগত্য করো তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76533,"position":19,"arabic":"إِنَّكُمْ","translation":"(তবে)তোমরাও নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76534,"position":20,"arabic":"لَمُشْرِكُونَ","translation":"অবশ্যই মুশরিক","audioUrl":"wbw/006_121_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76535,"position":21,"arabic":"١٢١","translation":"(১২১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":122,"arabic":"أَوَمَن كَانَ مَيْتًۭا فَأَحْيَيْنَٰهُ وَجَعَلْنَا لَهُۥ نُورًۭا يَمْشِى بِهِۦ فِى ٱلنَّاسِ كَمَن مَّثَلُهُۥ فِى ٱلظُّلُمَٰتِ لَيْسَ بِخَارِجٍۢ مِّنْهَا ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ زُيِّنَ لِلْكَٰفِرِينَ مَا كَانُوا۟ يَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"IS THEN -HE who was dead [in spirit] and whom We thereupon gave life, and for whom We set up a light whereby he might see his way among men - [is then he] like one [who is lost] in darkness deep, out of which he cannot emerge? [But] thus it is: goodly seem all their own doings to those who deny the truth.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/911.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":76659,"position":1,"arabic":"أَوَمَن","translation":"কি যে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_122_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76660,"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_122_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76661,"position":3,"arabic":"مَيْتًۭا","translation":"মৃত","audioUrl":"wbw/006_122_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76662,"position":4,"arabic":"فَأَحْيَيْنَـٰهُ","translation":"অতঃপর আমরা জীবিত করেছি তাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_122_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76663,"position":5,"arabic":"وَجَعَلْنَا","translation":"এবং আমরা দিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/006_122_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76664,"position":6,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","translation":"জন্যে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/006_122_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76665,"position":7,"arabic":"نُورًۭا","translation":"আলো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_122_007.mp3","charTy